title: Shocking Leaked Tesla Documents Hint at Cybertruck Problems
description: The EV giant is under pressure to launch new products, but a huge dump of confidential files in Germany details a litany of technical failings.

title: Everyone Wants to Regulate AI. No One Can Agree How
description: US lawmakers and CEOs alike say new rules are needed to prevent artificial intelligence from doing harm. So far, there are more wish lists than laws.

title: Temu Is Losing Millions of Dollars to Send You Cheap Socks
description: The Chinese shopping app is topping app stores in the US. But it’s burning money and squeezing its suppliers to a breaking point in a bid to take on Amazon.

title: Deepfakes, Cheapfakes, and Twitter Censorship Mar Turkey’s Elections
description: As the main candidates head to a runoff, disinformation is running riot on Turkish social media.
